gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Clippers 106, Rockets 100
gameRecap.excerpt: The Clippers snapped a 6-game losing streak to defeat the Rockets, 106-100 and improve to 4-7 on the year and 1-2 in West Group B Play. James Harden led the Clippers with 24 points, nine rebounds, and seven assists as Kawhi Leonard (26 points, eight rebounds) and Paul George (23 points, eight rebounds) totaled 49 points. Alperen Segun led Houston with 23 points, eight rebounds, and four assists while Fred VanVleet totaled 19 points, 10 assists, and eight rebounds. The Rockets move to 6-4 and 1-1 in West Group B Play.
